AzmeriFabricationDespair.description: Curse all targets in an area after a short delay, lowering their Chaos Resistance.
AzmeriFabricationDespair.name: Despair

AzmeriFabricationEnfeeble.description: Curse all targets in an area after a short delay, making them deal less damage.
AzmeriFabricationEnfeeble.name: Enfeeble

AzmeriFabricationTemporalChains.description: Curse all enemies in an area, Slowing them and making other effects on them expire more slowly.
AzmeriFabricationTemporalChains.name: Temporal Chains

AzmeriPictBowRainOfSpores.description: Fire arrows into the air that rain down around the targeted area, dealing damage to enemies they hit and creating spore pods where they land. Each spore pod deals chaos damage over time to nearby enemies and slows their movement speed. The pods last for a duration before bursting, dealing area damage.
AzmeriPictBowRainOfSpores.name: Toxic Rain

BloodMageBloodTendrils.description: Expel your own blood as Chaining blood tendrils in a cone in front of you. Enemies hit by the tendrils take Physical damage and are inflicted with a Debuff that deals Physical damage over time.
BloodMageBloodTendrils.name: Exsanguinate

GoreChargerCharge.description: Charges at an enemy, bashing it with the character's shield and striking it. This knocks it back and stuns it. Enemies in the way are pushed to the side. Damage and stun are proportional to distance travelled. Cannot be supported by Multistrike.
GoreChargerCharge.name: Charge

MMSBoneRabbleMortar.description: Generic monster mortar skill. Like Monster Projectile but has an impact effect.
MMSBoneRabbleMortar.name: Mortar

MMSHellscapeDemonEliteTripleMortar.description: Generic monster mortar skill. Like Monster Projectile but has an impact effect.
MMSHellscapeDemonEliteTripleMortar.name: Triple Mortar

MMSVaalGuardGrenade.description: Fire a bouncing Grenade that unleashes a devastating fiery blast when its fuse expires.
MMSVaalGuardGrenade.name: Explosive Grenade

MMSVaalGuardOilTrap.description: Fire a bouncing Grenade that bursts in a spray of Oil when the fuse expires or when it impacts an Enemy, dealing minimal damage but covering the ground and nearby enemies in Oil. Oil created this way can be Ignited by Detonator Skills or Ignited Ground.
MMSVaalGuardOilTrap.name: Oil Grenade

RisenArbalestRainOfArrows.description: Fires a large number of arrows into the air, to land in an area around the target after a short delay. Consumes your Frenzy Charges on use to fire additional arrows.
RisenArbalestRainOfArrows.name: Rain of Arrows

SerpentClanCurse.description: Curse all targets in an area after a short delay, making Hits against them ignore a portion of their Armour.
SerpentClanCurse.name: Vulnerability

ShellMonsterDeathMortar.description: Generic monster mortar skill. Like Monster Projectile but has an impact effect.
ShellMonsterDeathMortar.name: Death Mortar

ShellMonsterDeathMortarPoison.description: Generic monster mortar skill. Like Monster Projectile but has an impact effect.
ShellMonsterDeathMortarPoison.name: Death Mortar

ShellMonsterSprayMortar.description: Generic monster mortar skill. Like Monster Projectile but has an impact effect.
ShellMonsterSprayMortar.name: Mortar

ShellMonsterSprayMortarPoison.description: Generic monster mortar skill. Like Monster Projectile but has an impact effect.
ShellMonsterSprayMortarPoison.name: Mortar

SkelemancerSkelenado.description: Launch a spray of sparking Projectiles that travel erratically along the ground until they hit an enemy or expire.
SkelemancerSkelenado.name: Spark

TCHellscapePaleElite2Charge.name: Charge
